articles.title: Asia-Pacific markets mostly fall as investors parse China inflation data, await Fed decision - CNBC
articles.description: Asia-Pacific markets traded mostly lower on Wednesday as investors parse inflation data coming out of China later in the day, as well as await Fed decision.
